# Report Assistant — Project Context

## Purpose
Desktop Linux application (Qt6 + QML + C++17) for interactively assembling hardware-software compatibility reports (ЗОСРВ «Нейтрино» QNX-based OS). The app produces `.txt` files in a custom markup format consumed by a Jenkins-based report generator.

## Tech Stack
- **UI**: Qt6 + QML + Qt Quick Controls 2 (Material Dark theme)
- **Logic**: C++17 (`AppController`, `ReportEngine`, `ReportParser`, `PciAnalyzer`, `PresetManager`, `Storage`)
- **Storage**: JSON files via `Qt JSON` — no SQLite on MVP
- **Build**: CMake 3.20+
- **Target OS**: Ubuntu/Debian Linux (cross-distro via AppImage)

## Architecture
- `AppController` (QObject) — main bridge between QML and C++, exposed via `rootContext()->setContextProperty`
- `ReportEngine` — generates TXT markup from `ReportData` struct
- `ReportParser` — parses existing TXT files back into `ReportData`
- `PciAnalyzer` — parses QNX `pci -vvv` dump, looks up names in `pci.ids`
- `PresetManager` — loads/saves JSON presets (subsystems, drivers, interfaces, checks)
- `Storage` — reads/writes `.progress.json` alongside each `.txt` report file
- `SubsystemModel`, `PciDeviceModel`, `WorkItemModel` — QAbstractListModel subclasses

## Key Terminology
- **PID** = PCI Vendor ID (e.g., `8086` = Intel)
- **DID** = PCI Device ID (e.g., `7a62` = Raptor Lake SATA AHCI Controller)
- **Кастомная верстка** = the `.txt` markup format consumed by Jenkins to generate PDFs
- **Подсистема** = a hardware subsystem entry (Дисковая, Графическая, Сетевая, USB, Аудио, etc.)
- `OS_NAME` and `OS_VERSION` are **static tags** — never replaced by the app, substituted by Jenkins

## Report TXT Format (4 mandatory groups, in order)
```
@page "pas" <Title> (заводской номер <N>)
@brief
@par Содержание отчета: / @@item ...

@group device    — device params table + subsystems table (Controller | Interface | Driver)
@group report    — test results summary table (осинтаялция + all subsystems)
@group tests     — detailed @dl/@term/@use blocks per subsystem
@group recomendations — free text recommendations
```
- Unclosed `@table`, `@dl`, `@ul`, `@hint`, `@caution` → report generation fails
- `\n` inside a table cell = line break in rendered PDF (literal two-char sequence)
- Subsystem name in device table may contain `\n` (e.g., `Дисковая \n подсистема`)
- Subsystem name in report table and `@term` uses plain name without `\n`

## File Operations
- Open TXT → `ReportParser` reconstructs all form fields
- Save → `ReportEngine` regenerates TXT exactly
- Progress → autosaved as `filename.progress.json` (form state + Work tab notes)

